---
layout: base.njk
meta:
  title: "Frontier intelligence on AI"
  description: "Daily AI intelligence, strategy insights, and research recaps woven by TheLoomReport."
  type: "website"
---
<section class="hero">
  <span class="hero-badge">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
      <path d="M4 7h16M4 12h16M4 17h16" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" />
      <path d="M8 4v4M12 4v4M16 4v4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" />
    </svg>
    Daily loom briefing
  </span>
  <h1>Woven intelligence for the AI frontier</h1>
  <p class="hero-lede">Every morning, TheLoomReport spins a fresh briefing on AI breakthroughs, research, and market impact—crafted by agents, curated by humans.</p>
  <div class="hero-actions">
    <a href="{{ '/subscribe/' | url }}" class="btn">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="m5 7 7 5 7-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" fill="none" />
        <path d="M4 6h16a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v11a1 1 0 0 1-1 1H4a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V7a1 1 0 0 1 1-1Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" fill="none" />
      </svg>
      Subscribe to the digest
    </a>
    <a href="{{ '/topics/' | url }}" class="btn btn-ghost">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M5 5h14M5 12h14M5 19h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" />
      </svg>
      Explore topics
    </a>
  </div>
  <ul class="hero-highlights">
    <li>
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="m5 12 4 4 10-10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" fill="none" />
      </svg>
      Tactical insights distilled from the latest research drops.
    </li>
    <li>
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M5 4h14a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v14l-8-3-8 3V5a1 1 0 0 1 1-1Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" fill="none" stroke-linejoin="round" />
      </svg>
      Weekly digest summarizing what matters for operators.
    </li>
    <li>
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M12 6v12M6 12h12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" />
        <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" fill="none" />
      </svg>
      Human-in-the-loop editorial control with responsible AI guardrails.
    </li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section class="newsletter-callout">
  <div class="newsletter-callout__content">
    <span class="newsletter-callout__badge">Weekly Loom</span>
    <h2>Join the weekly loom</h2>
    <p>Every Monday we deliver the forces shaping AI—no noise, just field intelligence tailored for builders and operators.</p>
    <ul class="newsletter-callout__points">
      <li>
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="m5 12 4 4 10-10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" fill="none" />
        </svg>
        Strategic brief on regulation, funding, and platform shifts.
      </li>
      <li>
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M5 4h14a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v14l-8-3-8 3V5a1 1 0 0 1 1-1Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" fill="none" stroke-linejoin="round" />
        </svg>
        Curated research drops and product launches worth tracking.
      </li>
      <li>
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M12 6v12M6 12h12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" />
          <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" fill="none" />
        </svg>
        Operator playbook with responsible AI guardrails.
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="newsletter-callout__form">
    {% set variant = "callout" %}
    {% include "components/subscribe-form.njk" %}
    {% set variant = "stack" %}
  </div>
</section>

<section class="feature-section">
  <header>
    <h2>Latest dispatches</h2>
  </header>
  <div class="post-list">
    {% for post in collections.posts | slice(0, 6) %}
      <article class="post-item">
        <time datetime="{{ post.date | htmlDateString }}">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time>
        <h3><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h3>
        <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
        <ul class="tags">
          {% for tag in post.data.tags %}
            <li>#{{ tag }}</li>
          {% endfor %}
        </ul>
      </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
